generating sets, at 1.3-1.4 billion U.S. dollars, in the Rovno
Nuclear Power Station and Khmelynitsky Nuclear Power Station. The
building of the generating sets are precondition for Ukraine to
close down the Chernobyl Nuclear Power Station before 2000.
</P>
