Reports said the bank is now planning on 56 projects for
Ukraine with two billion U.S. dollars in investment. Half of the
fund will be channeled through Ukraine's banking system.
</P>
<P>
Ukraine has moved up within 1997 from the seventh position to
the fifth among debtors to the bank.
</P>
<P>
Reports said the bank is to hold a council meeting in the near
future to examine issues of modernizing Ukraine's navigation
system and establishing a first private foundation for Ukraine.
