<HEADLINE> Chinese Olympic Venturer Greeted on Return </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, November 27 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Olympic venturer Bu
Fanzhou attributed his success of his global tour to worldwide
supports when he told a celebration meeting and donation ceremony
here on Thursday.
</P>
<P>
Warmly welcomed on the gathering, which was held to mark his
successful return from the Centennial Olympic Tour, Bu said that
the collective wisdom was the most help through his global cycling.
</P>
<P>
"It's not only a result of combination of physical stamina and
frotitude, but coordination from the society -- colletive wisdom
is the most tremedous wisdom," he said.
</P>
<P>
