Greece at Athens, the birthplace of the modern Olympic Movement.
</P>
<P>
Touring cities of 17 countries where Summer Olympic Games were
held throughout the century, Bu wound up his journey on October 29
at 2000 Summer Olympics hosts Sydney, Australia.
</P>
<P>
