of surpassing one's self and others, which is the most important
Olympic spirit," said He Zhenliang, member of the Executive Board
of the International Olympic Committee.
</P>
<P>
At the ceremony the venturer donated all documents collected in
the tour on Olympic history to the Center for Olympic Study of
Beijing University of Physics Education, along with his bicycle,
which accompanied his historic journey, to the Sports Museum of
China. 
