<HEADLINE> Vietnam, Russia to Jointly Develop Oil, Gas Resources </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HANOI, November 27 (Xinhua) -- Vietnam and Russia have agreed
to jointly develop oil and gas resources in Vietnam, reported
media here today.
