<TEXT>
<P>
Calgary, Canada, November 26 (Xinhua) -- Chinese President
Jiang Zemin said here today that economic cooperation between
China and Alberta, Canada, has been growing fast in recent years
and is particularly fruitful in agriculture and energy.
</P>
<P>
"All these exchanges and cooperation have vigorously enhanced
mutual understanding and friendship, thus greatly pushing forward
the development of China-Canada relations," Jiang said.
</P>
