consulate general in Calgary. The new consulate general will be
the third one in Canada.
</P>
<P>
"I believe that with our concerted efforts," the friendly
relations and cooperation between China and Alberta will be
further strengthened, the Chinese president said.
</P>
<P>
Jiang is currently on a four-day state visit to Canada starting
here today.
</P>
<P>
In the coming days, Jiang said, he will exchange views with
Canadian leaders on developing bilateral relations and other
issues of mutual interest and have extensive contacts with people
of all walks of life in Canada.
</P>
<P>
"I believe that my current visit will help enhance the
friendship between our two peoples and promote the establishment
of a new type of cross-century friendly relations and cooperation
between our two countries," Jiang added. 
