Singida, Mwanza regions and other western and southern highland
areas, Mkapa said in the Urambo town.
</P>
<P>
Although Tabora is a major producer of tobacco which earns the
government a lot of foreign exchange, development of the region
is hindered by poor road conditions.
</P>
<P>
Mkapa told local residents that the African Development Bank
has agreed to fund the construction of the Itigi-Tabora road.
</P>
<P>
