<HEADLINE> Kazakhstan Makes Progress in Medical Insurance </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ALMA ATA, November 26 (Xinhua) -- Kazakhstan's compulsory
medical security system that started two years ago has been a
success, the Kazakhstan Pravda reported today.
</P>
<P>
