system, the highest percentage among republics in the Commonwealth
of Independent States.
</P>
<P>
In an interview with the newspaper, Talapker Imanbayev,
chairman of the government's Compulsory Medical Security Fund,
attributed the success to his country's earlier efforts in medical
security.
</P>
<P>
