pressure of the state budget. And since the advent of the system,
more clinics have been set up around the country, providing
health care for the populace.
</P>
<P>
Imanbayev said the new medical system fundamentally changed the
hospital's dependence on the state's financial allocation, helped
the introduction of market mechanism and raised the efficiency of
hospital operation. 
