<HEADLINE> Kyrgyzstan Elects New Lower House Speaker </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, November 26 (Xinhua) -- The Assembly of People's
Representatives of Kyrgyzstan (Lower House) today elected Abdygany
Erkebayevich Erkebayev as new Speaker, according to reports from
Bishkek, capital of Kyrgyzstan.
</P>
<P>
At today's meeting of the assembly, Erkebayev, 46, former Prime
