<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, November 23 (Xinhua) -- Following is a table showing
China's top three areas of Sino-foreign equity joint-ventures in
terms of trade volume in August this year, according to statistics
released by China's General Administration of Customs:
</P>
<P>
 value unit: USD 1,000
</P>
