<HEADLINE> Major News Items In Leading Australian Newspapers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CANBERRA, November 27 (Xinhua) -- The following are major news
items in leading Australian newspapers today:
</P>
<P>
The Australian
</P>
<P>
-- APEC's 18 leaders yesterday backed a surprise initiative to
deliver a global response to the currency market crisis which has
